{"tid":2136662,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"乜撚野叫方艙醫院？","createTime":"2020-08-02T10:17:14.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-02T10:49:37.000Z","uid":203867,"like":11,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"7b222bef623f35e09a837dba86067ba058a5fff5","tid":2136662,"uid":203867,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-02T10:17:14.000Z","msg":"叫組合屋/模組化/臨時/貨櫃醫院唔得嘅<br />\n係要講匪語以為咁樣好撚前衛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n遲下使唔使改口連乘客都變人員？"},{"pid":"d52f559cd552873eac86661de85ce090a4d73259","tid":2136662,"uid":307619,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-02T10:17:47.000Z","msg":"<span class=\"x-large\">空姐牛肉飯影相手足被控襲警 <br />\n聽朝9:30西九龍裁判法院提堂</span><br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2136461\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2136461</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/RzbrTe9.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FRzbrTe9.jpg&h=4dde1260&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/evWoa1T.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FevWoa1T.jpg&h=1a1d615b&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"dc32a5a76ca9668d5ee210c56edc95bc5f4a74b3","tid":2136662,"uid":179292,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-02T10:19:15.000Z","msg":"黃立䱽D Fd 嚟，可以蒸嚟食"},{"pid":"5f7d753c71b85a0167f1594a5939dbf9176e4dd4","tid":2136662,"uid":203867,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-02T10:20:02.000Z","msg":"「方艙」是中國大陸的工程術語，所指的結構也可稱為模塊（module）或預製式（prefabricated）結構。模塊建築結構的長處在於靈活性，因此一般採用標準的尺寸規格，其中最常見的規格是標準跨模式集裝箱（貨櫃）（Intermodal container），因此在西方使用模塊或預製式的箱式結構建造的模塊集成建築（Modular building）（裝配式建築、組合屋）一般通稱為「貨櫃xx」，例如「貨櫃住宅」（container home）。<br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"gold\">From wiki</span>"},{"pid":"c0e615299c58751c34325864e108f71425a40046","tid":2136662,"uid":53062,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-02T10:20:10.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/gf